Class Ingredient

  • java.lang.Object
    • Ingredient

  • public class Ingredient
extends java.lang.Object
    The Ingredient class represents an item used in a menu item and is useful for inventory management. It stores information about the item's ID, name, quantity, restock price, and threshold. This class provides a convenient way to work with ingredient data and perform operations such as setting and retrieving the item's attributes.
    Since:
    Oct 16, 2023
